</li>
<li>
<p>StackOverflow에서도 도움이 되는 자료가 많다: <a href="http://stackoverflow.com/questions/6861881"><em class="hyperlink">http://stackoverflow.com/questions/6861881</em></a></p>
</li>
</ul></section><div id="nav"><a href="/book/ko/%EC%95%A0%ED%94%8C%EB%A6%AC%EC%BC%80%EC%9D%B4%EC%85%98%EC%97%90-Git-%EB%84%A3%EA%B8%B0-Libgit2">prev</a> | <a href="/book/ko/v2/Git-%EB%AA%85%EB%A0%B9%EC%96%B4-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98%EC%99%80-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95">next</a></div></div>
